  "prompt": "What are the best Hindi songs to sing?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" Hindi songs to sing can be subjective, as it depends on personal taste, vocal range, and the mood you're aiming for. However, here\u2019s a mix of classic and contemporary Hindi songs across various genres that are widely loved and great for singing:\n\n### **Classic Bollywood Songs**  \n1. **\"Tum Hi Ho\"** - *Aashiqui 2* (Romantic)  \n2. **\"Lag Ja Gale\"** - *Woh Kaun Thi?* (Melancholic)  \n3. **\"Tere Bina Zindagi Se\"** - *Aandhi* (Devotional/Romantic)  \n4. **\"Yeh Jo Mohabbat Hai\"** - *Kati Patang* (Romantic)  \n5. **\"Chura Liya Hai Tumne\"** - *Yaadon Ki Baaraat* (Fun and Energetic)  \n\n### **Romantic Songs**  \n6. **\"Pehla Nasha\"** - *Jo Jeeta Wohi Sikandar* (Soft and Dreamy)  \n7. **\"Tum Se Hi\"** - *Jab We Met* (Soulful)  \n8. **\"Teri Mitti\"** - *Kesari* (Patriotic/Romantic)  \n9. **\"Phir Bhi Tumko Chahunga\"** - *Half Girlfriend* (Emotional)  \n10. **\"Raabta\"** - *Agent Vinod* (Melodious)  \n\n### **Upbeat and Fun Songs**  \n11. **\"Galiyan\"** - *Ek Villain* (Energetic)  \n12. **\"Tumhi Ho Bandhu\"** - *Cocktail* (Cheerful)  \n13. **\"Badtameez Dil\"** - *Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani* (Fun and Playful)  \n14. **\"Bole Chudiyan\"** - *Kabhi Khushi Kabhie Gham* (Festive)  \n15. **\"Jeene Laga Hoon\"** - *Ramaiya Vastavaiya* (Upbeat Romantic)  \n\n### **Sad and Emotional Songs**  \n16. **\"Tujhe Bhula Diya\"** - *Anjaana Anjaani* (Heartbreak)  \n17. **\"Kal Ho Naa Ho\"** - *Kal Ho Naa Ho* (Bittersweet)  \n18. **\"Agar Tum Saath Ho\"** - *Tamasha* (Emotional)  \n19. **\"Jo Bheji Thi Dua\"** - *Shanghai* (Soulful)  \n20. **\"Kuch Toh Hua Hai\"** - *Kal Ho Naa Ho* (Melancholic)  \n\n### **Sufi and Spiritual Songs**  \n21. **\"Kun Faya Kun\"** - *Rockstar* (Sufi)  \n22. **\"Maula Mere Maula\"** - *Anwar* (Spiritual)  \n23. **\"Khwabon Ke Parindey\"** - *Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara* (Dreamy)  \n24. **\"Chaap Tilak\"** - *Abida Parveen* (Sufi)  \n25. **\"Alvida\"** - *Life in a Metro* (Soulful)  \n\n### **Contemporary Songs**  \n26. **\"Kalank\"** - *Kalank* (Melancholic)  \n27. **\"Gerua\"** - *Dilwale* (Romantic)  \n28. **\"Galliyan\"** - *Ek Villain* (Emotional)  \n29. **\"Bekhayali\"** - *Kabir Singh* (Intense)  \n30. **\"Shayad\"** - *Love Aaj Kal* (Dreamy)  \n\n### Timeless Oldies  \n31. **\"Mera Joota Hai Japani\"** - *Shree 420* (Patriotic/Fun)  \n32. **\"Pyar Hua Iqraar Hua\"** - *Shree 420* (Romantic)  \n33. **\"Kabhi Kabhi Mere Dil Mein\"** - *Kabhi Kabhi* (Romantic)  \n34. **\"Chandan Sa Badan\"** - *Saraswatichandra* (Melodious)  \n35. **\"Zindagi Bhar Nahin Bhoolegi\"** - *Barsaat Ki Raat* (Classic Melody)  \n\nThese songs cater to different moods and vocal styles, so you can choose based on what resonates with you. Whether you're performing at a gathering or simply singing for fun, these tracks are sure to impress!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
